Package: pkern
Title: Fast Kriging with Product Kernels
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Dean",
           family = "Koch",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dkoch@ualberta.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8849-859X"))
Description: This package is a collection of functions for fitting geostatistical models with
separable covariance functions. It uses kronecker product representations of the covariance
matrix and its submatrices to speed up calculations related to likelihood and conditional mean.
